<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Novo Anime Adicionado: <%= animeTitulo %></title>
    <style> body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; } .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #151515; color: #f9f9f9; } .header { background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center; } .header img { max-width: 180px; } .content { padding: 30px; } .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #E50914; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; } .footer { background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5; } h1, p { margin: 0 0 20px 0; } h1 { font-size: 24px; color: #ffffff; } p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; } </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #0A0A0A;">
    <center>
        <table class="container" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #151515; color: #f9f9f9;">
            <tr><td class="header" style="background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center;"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/your-logo.png" alt="DenyAnimeHub Logo"></td></tr>
            <tr><td><img src="<%= animeImagemCapa %>" alt="Capa de <%= animeTitulo %>" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; height: auto; display: block;"></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="content" style="padding: 30px;"><table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td><h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #ffffff; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Novo Anime no Catálogo!</h1><p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #c5c5c5; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Um novo título incrível acaba de chegar ao DenyAnimeHub. Confira os detalhes abaixo:</p><h2 style="font-size: 20px; color: #E50914; margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><%= animeTitulo %></h2><p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: #c5c5c5; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"><%= sinopse %></p></td></tr><tr><td align="center"><a href="<%= verUrl %>" target="_blank" class="button" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #E50914; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Ver Detalhes e Assistir</a></td></tr></table></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="footer" style="background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5;"><p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5;">Você está recebendo este e-mail porque se inscreveu para receber notificações no DenyAnimeHub.</p><p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5;"><a href="http://localhost:3000/editar-perfil" target="_blank" style="color: #c5c5c5; text-decoration: underline;">Gerenciar Preferências</a> | © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> DenyAnimeHub</p></td></tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>